A1 A2 are test scripts in developing process

faster_2 // faster_test // test_whisper // xxx.py are used to test basic funcs

kyle_faster_whisper.py is a relatively well-developed test script with gui


recording.py 是实现获取麦克风的音频，这个功能为实现实时翻译功能预留的
实时翻译功能在GUI是已经预留，但是没有具体集成实现

recording.py is used to get the audio from the microphone, which is reserved for real-time translation.
This function is reserved for the real-time translation function in the GUI, but it is not integrated into the implementation.

